title: 49ers coach Seifert crushed Super Bowl opponents in 1990, ’95
text:
Photo: Scott Sommerdorf, The Chronicle George Seifert achieved great things with the 49ers with the help of quarterbacks Steve Young and Joe Montana (center). George Seifert achieved great things with the 49ers with the help...
Even in retirement, far removed from the piercing spotlight and smothering pressure of life as an NFL head coach, George Seifert remains sheepish about his triumphs.
